ost important problems learning we are driven by ideas rooted in imagination and innovation a steadfast curiosity to attain new skills perspectives and knowledge we embrace feedback and opportunities for selfimprovement that improve and transform the environment around us teamwork we demand a culture of collaboration where we work with exceptionally talented colleagues whom we are fortunate to learn from and be inspired by every single day we seek each other’s opinions and ideas share in our success and learn from our failures we achieve more together than we ever could on our own benefits investing in your growth continuous learning our dedicated learning and development team matches employees with industry experts to provide personalized skill development our team members are encouraged to pursue advanced degrees with company reimbursement nourish  energize healthy foods and snacks keep our teams at peak performance after hours we host exclusive events for colleagues friends and family from box seats at stadiums to theater buyouts and cooking classes you will bond with colleagues at global and local events onsite fitness centers reach new levels of personal performance with access to fitness centers what our people say results of  great place to work survey  say colleagues are willing to give extra to get the job done  of employees say they are proud to tell others they work here  feel a sense of pride when they look at what we accomplish  say they felt welcomed when they joined the firm  say the firm is a friendly place to work  say they are given a lot of responsibility supporting our communities new computer labs at carnegie mellon partnering with carnegie mellon university citadel helped create the stateoftheart citadel teaching commons support includes technology to support research in machine learning distributed systems and parallel computing architecture read more kenneth griffin makes largest gift in harvard college history alumnus donates  million to principally support financial aid read more citadel service day more than  citadel team members joined together with family and friends to volunteer on citadel service day  organizations we serve we help our communities reach their full potential by creating meaningful sustainable outcomes we support more than  community partners with a special focus on education hunger and poverty relief and cultural and medical organizations across the globe while financial support is part of our effort the heart of citadel serves is our employees’ commitment to sharing their time and expertise last year our colleagues contributed more than  volunteer hours at events such as stocking food banks and building and delivering a child’s first bike to families in lowincome communities social media connect  learn facebook citadel securities twitter tweets by citsecurities instagram sometimes you need a multiterabyte database to bring a great idea to life other times a marker we like both draw the future with us a post shared by citadel securities citadelsecurities on apr   at pm pdt  open positions learn more citadel securities about citadel securities products public policy careers what’s new contact client login privacy policy terms of use notices disclosures  south dearborn street chicago il  usa copyright  citadel llc or one of its affiliates  all rights reserved about citadel securities products overview equities  options ficc public policy careers overview why citadel securities open positions internships on campus what’s new contact client login notices  citadel securities citadel securities about citadel securities products public policy careers what’s new contact client login notices “citadel” “citadel securities” the castle logo and “better markets make a better world” are service marks of an affiliate of citadel llc and are registered or are pending registration in the united states and several other jurisdictions citadel securities hong kong limited is exempt from the requiremen