el clears its high water mark the new york times   a b c amanda cantrell  december  are you prepared for the next crash institutional investors alpha   a b hurst georgina  june  a winning night for hedge fund managers and investors institutional investor retrieved  february    sorkin andrew ross stevenson alexandra  april  ben bernanke will work with citadel a hedge fund as an adviser new york times retrieved  april    anderson jenny  july  hedge fund forced to sell its portfolio the new york times  accessdate requires url help  craig susanne karnitschnig matthew berman dennis  november  why citadel pounced on wounded etrade wall street journal retrieved  july    comstock courtney  july  read the angry letter ken griffins citadel sent to the etrade board business insider retrieved  july    philbin brett  march  etrade loses largest shareholder as citadel sells out wall street journal retrieved  july    a b risk  firms of the future citadel risknet august   retrieved july     a b michael mackenzie tom braithwaite september   derivatives trading safer and more efficient says citadel financial times retrieved july     paul merrion july   ban highspeed trading absolutely not says citadels griffin crains chicago business retrieved july     citadel conversations retrieved july     carr robert october   citadel center trades in m transaction globest retrieved   dearborn center announces squarefoot  m lease with citadel beitler re corp march   retrieved   citadel renews top six floors at namesake tower national real estate investor  november    global locations citadel retrieved  february    success stories greater chicago food depository retrieved august     citadel and national museum of mathematics partner to offer nocost visit to museum prweb january   retrieved august     shia kapos march   not the ken griffin story you were expecting crains chicago business retrieved july     taub stephen the hedge fund report card pdf institutional investors alpha retrieved  march   